TECHNICAL TASK


Hyper Helios
Develop a Django application where it will display a list of data in a table.

Requirements: (Must fulfill)

=> There will be a form with two fields: a) Name b) Phone number.
=> The design should be responsive.
=> We would like to respect your creativity in UI design.
=> Push the code to a GitHub repository.
=> Every git commit should be relevant and meaningful.
=> The phone number field will only accept BD phone numbers with a country
   code. If the phone number is invalid, the phone number field should show an
   inline error (below the field).
=> There will be a detail page for each row, and the route path will be "/contact/
   id".

Constraints:
=> You should not use HTML Table tags for the data table.
=> You have to write raw CSS for styling (No framework).
